title: Gaoba gao krush banna nwngswr
lyrics:
Gaoba gao krush banna nwngswr
Dhwrwmni lamayao agan surdw -2
Kapalao Bikayao Jwngha Krushni Hangkw-4
(A)
Nwngswr sinai janai nonthara
Krushni biban banna bla-2
Sushra Jadw arw phusob jadw-2
(B)
Nwngswr papjwng dagele thar swi
Nonga bla adri jagwn -2
Sushra Jadw arw phusob jadw-2
